{
  "info": {
    "name": "Vero2 Real Estate Service",
    "description": "Postman collection for Real Estate Service (Port 3011)\n\n**ROLES & ACCESS:**\n- **Public Routes**: No authentication required\n- **User/Agency Routes**: Use `user_token` (from POST /sso/auth/user/login)\n  - Users and agencies can CREATE properties\n- **Admin Routes**: Use `admin_token` (from POST /sso/auth/admin/login)\n  - Admins can MANAGE visibility, update, delete, and reorder properties\n  - Admins can CREATE and MANAGE categories\n\n**IMPORTANT:**\n- Visibility endpoint REQUIRES admin token (admin-only operation)\n- Creating properties REQUIRES user token (user/agency operation)\n- Properties support multiple photos, price filtering, and property-specific fields",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.1"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3013",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Base URL for Real Estate Service (Port 3013 for testing, or 8000 for production via Kong)"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_prefix",
      "value": "api/real-estate",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "admin_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT Bearer token from SSO Service (admin role required)"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT Bearer token from SSO Service (for user routes if needed)"
    },
    {
      "key": "property_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Property ID from create property response"
    },
    {
      "key": "category_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Category ID from create category response"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Check service health status"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Properties - Public",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Visible Properties",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties?page=1&limit=10&propertyType=&propertyStatus=&minPrice=&maxPrice=&category=&isVisible=",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Page number"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10",
                  "description": "Items per page"
                },
                {
                  "key": "propertyType",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by property type (e.g., Houses, Flats, Apartments)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "propertyStatus",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by property status (Rent, Buy, Sale, Mortgage)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "minPrice",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Minimum price filter"
                },
                {
                  "key": "maxPrice",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Maximum price filter"
                },
                {
                  "key": "category",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by category name"
                },
                {
                  "key": "isVisible",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filter by visibility (admin only)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Get all visible real estate properties (Public). Only visible properties are returned. Supports filtering by property type, status, price range, and category."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Property by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties/{{property_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties", "{{property_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Get single property details by property ID (Public). Only visible properties are returned."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Properties - Shared User/Agency/Business",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Property (Shared)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.propertyId) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('property_id', response.propertyId);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{user_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"propertyType\": \"Houses\",\n  \"propertyStatus\": \"Sale\",\n  \"currentStatus\": \"Ready-to-Move\",\n  \"photos\": [\n    \"https://example.com/photo1.jpg\",\n    \"https://example.com/photo2.jpg\"\n  ],\n  \"description\": \"Beautiful 3-bedroom house in prime location with modern amenities\",\n  \"sizeSquareFeet\": 2000,\n  \"price\": 500000,\n  \"features\": [\n    \"Air conditioning\",\n    \"Parking\",\n    \"Gym\",\n    \"Pool\"\n  ],\n  \"beds\": 3,\n  \"bathroom\": 2,\n  \"kitchen\": 1,\n  \"category\": \"Residential\",\n  \"displayOrder\": 1,\n  \"isVisible\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties"]
            },
            "description": "Create new real estate property (User/Agency/Business).\n\n✅ Users, agencies, and businesses can call this generic endpoint.\n⚠️ Requires a valid `user_token`.\n\n**Property Types:** Houses, Flats, Apartments, Townhouses, Villas, Condominiums, Office Buildings, Stores, Shopping Malls, Hotel, Resorts, etc.\n**Property Status:** Rent, Buy, Sale, Mortgage\n**Current Status:** Vacant, Currently Rented, Under Construction, Ready-to-Move\n**Residential Fields:** beds, bathroom, kitchen (for residential properties only)"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Properties - User",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Property (User Only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{user_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"propertyType\": \"Flats\",\n  \"propertyStatus\": \"Rent\",\n  \"currentStatus\": \"Vacant\",\n  \"photos\": [\n    \"https://example.com/flat-photo.jpg\"\n  ],\n  \"description\": \"Spacious 2-bedroom flat available for rent\",\n  \"sizeSquareFeet\": 1200,\n  \"price\": 1500,\n  \"features\": [\n    \"Air conditioning\",\n    \"Parking\",\n    \"Lift / Elevator\"\n  ],\n  \"beds\": 2,\n  \"bathroom\": 1,\n  \"kitchen\": 1,\n  \"category\": \"Residential\",\n  \"isVisible\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties/user",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties", "user"]
            },
            "description": "Create property restricted to **accountType = user**. Fails with 403 if token belongs to agency/business."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Property (User Owns)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{user_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"description\": \"Updated property description\",\n  \"price\": 1600,\n  \"currentStatus\": \"Currently Rented\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties/user/{{property_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties", "user", "{{property_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update property owned by the authenticated **user** account. Fails with 403 if property was created by another account or token is not user type."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Property (User Owns)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{user_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/{{api_prefix}}/properties/user/{{property_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties", "user", "{{property_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Delete a property created by the authenticated **user**. Returns 403 if property belongs to another account or token type mismatch."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
