              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["{{api_prefix}}", "properties", "{{property_id}}", "reorder"]
            },
            "description": "Move property up in the list (Admin). Swaps display order with property above. Each row has Up (↑) and Down (↓) arrow buttons. Reordering is saved instantly."
